Maybe we all need to help each other to change the way we celebrate. Hollywood puts all these commercials on about buying more stuff for Christmas, maybe we just need to find ways to share Christ in a simple way. This year we are giving out homemade ornaments made from our chicken eggs. We put bible verses on them or Merry Christmas. We made our gifts and they came from our hearts. It didn't cost much but our time. They were liked so much I got an order to make them for somebody else to give away for gifts, which helped our family financially. Merry Christmas.
